{"tid":557264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[估結局]金融IT男付60多萬首期 認購買新世界首置盤三房單位","createTime":"2018-02-11T07:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T08:36:56.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"3944d2fab81ded3c3df639b1aff7be5112d63d12","tid":557264,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T07:40:12.000Z","msg":"現年31歲的傅先生今早到荃灣愉景新城的售樓處揀樓，他透露現與家人於粉嶺居住，月租約2萬元。他今次支付約60多萬的首期，購買一個三房單位，計劃與太太及小朋友組織家庭。<br />\n<br />\n從事<span style=\"color: red;\">金融科技</span>的他稱，用了3年時間儲起這筆首期，嘆大部分年輕人均無法負擔首期而無法「上車」，「𠵱家租樓都要2萬，仲可能貴過供樓。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/158992/%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C15%E4%BC%99%E9%A6%96%E7%BD%AE%E7%9B%A4%E5%8D%8A%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E5%85%A7%E7%8D%B2%E8%AA%8D%E8%B3%BC-%E8%B2%B7%E5%AE%B6-%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E7%95%80%E5%94%94%E8%B5%B7%E9%AB%98%E6%98%82%E9%A6%96%E6%9C%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F158992%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C15%25E4%25BC%2599%25E9%25A6%2596%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E7%259B%25A4%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%2585%25A7%25E7%258D%25B2%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25B3%25BC-%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25BC%2595%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2595%2580%25E5%2594%2594%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2598%2582%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%259C%259F&d=XcvNY2S5fmIe3NJrS%2F6R9TPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=c6bbdf18\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/158992/%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C15%E4%BC%99%E9%A6%96%E7%BD%AE%E7%9B%A4%E5%8D%8A%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E5%85%A7%E7%8D%B2%E8%AA%8D%E8%B3%BC-%E8%B2%B7%E5%AE%B6-%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E7%95%80%E5%94%94%E8%B5%B7%E9%AB%98%E6%98%82%E9%A6%96%E6%9C%9F</a>"},{"pid":"b8758c31ec6d359c03f4670bdf9059dbbbe37b37","tid":557264,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T07:41:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" cla